 1999-01341999-02-040,  HERITAGE,  ,  , 
PrecisOrder fixing THURSDAY, APRIL 1, 1999, as the day upon which the PARKS CANADA SECTOR of the Department of Canadian Heritage is deemed to be severed from the Department and become a part of the Parks Canada Agency, for the purposes of section 48.1 of the Public Service Staff Relations Act.
